nodes.text: A minor moon in the galaxy was part of a family story of the Starros clan. According to the story, Caden Starros, the great-grandfather of Avon Starros, had once been stranded on the moon by an enemy who stole his starship. After getting off the moon, Caden had tracked the enemy all the way to Orondia to have revenge. Avon remembered the story after the destruction of the cruiser Steady Wing, although it was unclear whether or not it was true.
